Package org.wmn4j.notation

Class MultiStaffPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wmn4j.notation.MultiStaffPart
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Measure>, Part
    public final class MultiStaffPart
extends java.lang.Object
implements Part
    Represents a score part with multiple staves such as are often used with keyboard instruments.

    This class is immutable.
